text: The Australian Federation Party was a small right-wing political party in Australia. ==History== ===Australian Country Alliance=== The Australian Country Alliance (or ACA) was a small political party in Victoria, Australia. It was started in 2004 as an alternative to the National Party in Victoria. In 2014, the Victoria branch of the Katter's Australian Party merged with the Country Alliance. == References == Category:2004 establishments in Australia Category:Political parties in Australia
